sub_title: Tutor in English Language Skills at Private Practice
summary:
Experienced Teacher English and tutoring ("bijles") in English Language skills in The Netherlands on several levels: MAVO, HAVO, VWO and College. Experienced also in teaching English as a Second Language (HAN University, Nijmegen).
Demonstrated history of working in the hospitality industry. Skilled in Business Planning, Coaching, Event Management, Team Building, and Marketing. 
Strong business development professional with a Bachelor of Education (B.Ed.) focused on Teaching English as a Second or Foreign Language/ESL Language Instructor from E.v. Amsterdam.
